<p>
<lb n="1"/>cōpakiru<unclear>tu</unclear> varu<hi rend="grantha">ṣam</hi> Irāca Irācava
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ḷa nāṭṭup paṉṟi cūḻ nāṭṭu Aḻimpinā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>yiṉār yirā<supplied reason="omitted">cēntira</supplied> cōḷīcuramuṭai<supplied reason="omitted">ya</supplied> nāyaṉāṟkut
<lb n="4"/>tāṉava ṉāṭṭu neṭuvācal cīmaikkuk kaṟuttā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>vāṉa pāṇṭiya perumāḷāṉa māvuli vāṇā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>tarāyar makkaḷil tirumēṉiyaḻakiyarāṉa kulacē
<lb n="7" break="no"/>karak kāliṅkarāyarum paḻaiya vaṉapperumāḷāṉa
<lb n="8" break="no"/>cīvalakkāliṅkirāyarum centāmaraikaṇṇa
<lb n="9" break="no"/>rum Immūvarumōm vīrarācēntira cōḷīcuramuṭai
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ya nāyaṉāṟkut tiruṉāmattukkāṇi Āka viṭṭa nilam
<lb n="11"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> vatuk kaṇṭiyūr vayal kīḻaivayalil ceṭṭiyaḷ
<lb n="12"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> Oṇṭi Uṟai <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
